        <h2>1. Introduction and Acceptance</h2>
        <p><strong>1.1</strong> These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the FutureProof Financial platform ("Platform") and the Equity Preservation Mortgage ("EPM") products and services offered by FutureProof Financial Ltd ("we", "us", "our", "FutureProof").</p>
        <p><strong>1.2</strong> By accessing the Platform, creating an account, or applying for an EPM product, you ("you", "your", "the Borrower") confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms, together with our Privacy Policy and any supplementary documentation provided during the application process.</p>
        <p><strong>1.3</strong> If you do not agree to these Terms, you must not use the Platform or apply for any EPM product.</p>
        <p><strong>1.4</strong> These Terms are provided in addition to, and do not replace, any specific mortgage offer, Key Facts Illustration, or contractual documentation you receive in connection with an EPM application.</p>
        <p><strong>1.5</strong> We recommend that you obtain independent legal and financial advice before entering into any EPM arrangement.</p>
