        <p><strong>4.2</strong> FutureProof Financial Ltd is registered with Companies House, registration number [TBD], with its registered office in England.</p>
        <p><strong>4.3</strong> Our authorisation covers home finance mediation and administration activities as defined by the Financial Services and Markets Act 2000 (FSMA) and the associated Regulated Activities Order.</p>
        <p><strong>4.4</strong> We comply with the FCA Handbook, including but not limited to:</p>
