        <p><strong>9.3</strong> All fees will be disclosed in full before you are required to commit to the application. You will not be charged any hidden fees.</p>
        <p><strong>9.4</strong> We will provide you with a European Standardised Information Sheet (ESIS) where applicable, in accordance with the Mortgage Credit Directive.</p>
