          <li>(b) <strong>Consumer Credit Act 1974 (as amended):</strong> Which provides protections in relation to credit agreements, including rights of withdrawal and requirements for adequate pre-contractual information;</li>
          <li>(c) <strong>Financial Services and Markets Act 2000:</strong> Which establishes the regulatory framework within which we operate;</li>
          <li>(d) <strong>Unfair Contract Terms Act 1977:</strong> Which restricts the extent to which liability can be excluded or restricted by contract terms;</li>
          <li>(e) <strong>Equality Act 2010:</strong> We do not discriminate on the basis of any protected characteristic.</li>
