        <h2>15. Cooling-Off Period</h2>
        <p><strong>15.1</strong> In accordance with FCA rules, you have a cooling-off period of <%= details[:cooling_off] %> from the date you receive your mortgage offer within which you may withdraw from the agreement without penalty.</p>
        <p><strong>15.2</strong> To exercise your right to withdraw, you must notify us in writing (by email or post) within the cooling-off period. The withdrawal takes effect from the date we receive your notification.</p>
        <p><strong>15.3</strong> If you withdraw during the cooling-off period:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>(a) Any funds already advanced will be repaid in full;</li>
          <li>(b) Any fees paid (other than the valuation fee, if the valuation has already been conducted) will be refunded;</li>
          <li>(c) No early repayment charges will apply.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>15.4</strong> The cooling-off period does not apply to subsequent variations of the mortgage terms agreed by both parties after the initial offer.</p>
